The *~BlogJournal* [[Help:WikiPlugin|plugin]] includes the latest blog entries for the current users blog if signed, or the ADMIN_USER's blog if not.

== Usage

{{{
<<BlogJournal>>
}}}

== Arguments

{| class="bordered"
|-
! Argument
! Description
! Default value
|-
| <b>count</b>
| Number of entries
| empty
|-
| <b>user</b>
| Blog of given user
| empty
|-
| <b>month</b>
| List the blog titles per month
| empty
|}

== Example

{{{
<<BlogJournal>>
}}}

<<BlogJournal>>

